'''第67届[[威尼斯电影节|威尼斯电影节]]'''于[[2010年电影|2010年]]9月1日至9月11日在[[意大利|意大利]][[威尼斯|威尼斯]]举行。<ref name="labiennale.org">{{cite web |url=http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema |title=67th Venice International Film Festival |accessdate=2010-05-07 |work=labiennale.org |date=2010-05-07 |archive-date=2010-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100419235848/http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema |dead-url=no }}</ref>开幕影片是[[戴倫·艾洛諾夫斯基|戴倫·艾洛諾夫斯基]]导演的《[[黑天鹅_(电影)|黑天鹅]]》，闭幕影片是[[朱丽·泰莫|朱丽·泰莫]]（Julie Taymor）的《[[暴风雨_(2010电影)|暴风雨]]》，兩部片均產自美國。<ref>{{cite journal | last=Lyman | first=Eric J. | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3i4c15c030a696fa142f87203f980fdbe3 | title=Aronofsky's 'Black Swan' to open Venice fest | journal=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | date=July 22, 2010 | access-date=2010-09-04 | archive-date=2010-07-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100723161739/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3i4c15c030a696fa142f87203f980fdbe3 | dead-url=no }}</ref>美國导演[[昆廷·塔伦蒂诺|昆廷·塔伦蒂诺]]出任评委会主席。<ref name="Jury">{{cite web |url=http://www.m1905.com/news/20100730/362731.shtml |title=力推新人的威尼斯：67届威尼斯国际电影节前瞻 |accessdate=2010-07-30 |work=m1905.com |date=2010-09-04 |archive-date=2010-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100801133428/http://www.m1905.com/news/20100730/362731.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

香港導演[[吳宇森|吳宇森]]獲頒終身成就金獅獎。<ref name="labiennale Woo">{{cite web |url=http://www.labiennale.org/en/news/woo.html |title=John Woo to receive Golden Lion award in Sept. 2010 |accessdate=2010-06-17 |work=labiennale.org |date=2010-05-07 |archive-date=2010-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100408105239/http://www.labiennale.org/en/news/woo.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

